column4: NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "3C375B964AA80B0987D6DBBFC3A9BE1B", "Did you see the Eastern Bridge fixed? We worked so hard.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "833475AB43A150B900F5B099B22CD582", "We\'re fixing Digital Bridge now. Please wait a while.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "BC4E2BFD4DF5298DDAF3BCA54052791C", "I hear there\'s a rare Digimon at Coela Point in the south.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "79D058D248B8EF5A7D91988EDE4C5838", "Rumor has it is that he shows up late afternoon everyday.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "263BCBBC4686AB8EBA73AA93EA4DA69D", "Say, did you know there\'s a broken bridge in the east part of the city?")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "4E10BBAB4DB2F2E1541062850B098DB4", "We didn\'t think anyone would ever use it, so we didn\'t do anything about it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "FDE7AE294E1F46E7E7818F9F1C9A1C5D", "We\'re thinking about fixing it on our own.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "05A998C24DE9F14C81AFF7B3B2F68D2F", "Until then, go check the west and south sections. Then come back and see me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "E2D579AD43FCD57298EDB4A64CE080D4", "Did you go to Geko Swamp? A mischievous Digimon may trick you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[3881A5D242F5C7DF1B7519BB485C8D2E]", "26086CD74E8D694EC3EF8D80D1E78A7A", "Once a Digimon digivolves, remember, his Technique Sets will change.")
